" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/vtuber_dokibird_reached_youtube_subscribers_500k.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/vtuber_dokibird_reached_youtube_subscribers_500k.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/vtuber_dokibird_reached_youtube_subscribers_500k.png" alt="" class="wp-image-115398"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> 2月5日，NIJISANJI EN的运营公司ANYCOLOR针对据称是Dokibird的表演者/声音模特的<strong>Seren Ryugetsu</strong>发表了一份声明，称“ <em><a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多次违反合同并在SNS上发布误导性虚假信息”。</a></em>宣布由于<em><a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">“他的行为</a></em>”，合同将被终止。此外，虽然ANYCOLOR在海外受到了猛烈批评，包括<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称“<em>对业务结果的影响将极其轻微</em>”，但已经采取了</a>支持Dokibird的行动，并订阅了该名人的官方YouTube频道。许多人参加了这次活动事件接二连三。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="674" data-attachment-id="115402" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-reached-youtube-subscribers-500k/vtuber_dokibird_youtube_channel_february_13_2024/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/vtuber_dokibird_youtube_channel_february_13_2024.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_dokibird_youtube_channel_february_13_2024" data-image-description="&lt;p>;Dokibird&lt;/p>;
" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;Dokibird&lt;/p>;
